  "title": "CAD DRAFTER",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<p>Prepare shop drawings based on approved working drawings.</p>\n<p>Knowledge of reading Architectural, C&amp;S and MEP services drawings.</p>\n<p>Knowledge of checking shop drawing is an advantage.</p>\n<p>Good to have knowledge of standards, guidelines, code of practice of local agencies in Singapore e.g., BCA, LTA , PUB etc</p>\n<p>Able to liaise with others design disciplines.</p>\n<p>Able to coordinate and be responsible for the quality of production of all submission drawings.</p>\n<p>Supervise the production of 2D drawings with accuracy ensuring drawings produced are according to the Office or the Client’s Drafting Standards and Procedures, and the drawing submission schedule is achieved.</p>\n<p>Work under the supervision of Engineer and perform work task assigned.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<p>1. Good knowledge in AUTOCAD drafting.</p>\n<p>2. Good communication skills.</p>\n<p>3. Experienced in working in a construction firm or in a design consultancy.</p>",
